WEBVTT

00:07.382 --> 00:08.972
<i>- Previously on "Chucky"...</i>

00:09.009 --> 00:10.219
[high-pitched]
I’m Chucky.

00:10.260 --> 00:11.720
[normal] And I’m your friend
till the end.

00:11.762 --> 00:15.392
<i>You get that now, Jake.
We all have our secrets.</i>

00:15.432 --> 00:18.892
I’m gonna go kill your sister.
Wanna come?

00:18.936 --> 00:20.646
<i>[suspenseful music]</i>

00:20.687 --> 00:22.607
You snooze, you lose.
<i>- Charles Lee Ray was</i>

00:22.648 --> 00:24.188
<i>a serial killer
who died in the ’80s.</i>

00:24.233 --> 00:25.863
He transferred his soul
to a Good Guy doll.

00:25.901 --> 00:27.241
<i>- Chucky is alive.</i>

00:27.277 --> 00:29.027
- This is a problem
we can solve together.

00:30.155 --> 00:31.405
- [grunting]

00:31.448 --> 00:33.868
- You have no idea
how hard it’s been

00:33.909 --> 00:36.909
<i>getting one
of you little shits to play.</i>

00:36.954 --> 00:39.214
- Chucky, it worked.

00:39.248 --> 00:40.918
- Jennifer Tilly!
- Hi!

00:40.958 --> 00:41.918
[cheers and applause]

00:41.959 --> 00:43.459
- Every Better Days Hospital

00:43.502 --> 00:46.132
in the country
will receive a priceless gift

00:46.171 --> 00:47.921
from her personal collection.

00:47.965 --> 00:49.265
- Junior!

00:49.299 --> 00:50.629
- [grunting]
[squishing]

00:52.302 --> 00:54.012
- No!
- We did it.

00:55.347 --> 00:56.557
- Drive!

01:00.310 --> 01:07.150
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

01:07.192 --> 01:08.402
- Are we there yet?

01:08.443 --> 01:11.953
- When do we get
to start stabbin’ people?

01:11.989 --> 01:13.949
- Wait, you got a knife?

01:13.991 --> 01:15.451
- Yeah, I got a knife.

01:15.492 --> 01:17.622
They passed ’em out
at orientation.

01:17.661 --> 01:19.451
- What the fuck?

01:21.164 --> 01:22.624
What?

01:22.666 --> 01:24.166
- [chuckles] What?

01:24.209 --> 01:26.959
I didn’t say anything.
[laughs]

01:27.004 --> 01:29.054
- Don’t worry.

01:29.089 --> 01:32.179
They say bald guys
are more virile.

01:32.217 --> 01:35.547
They say chicks
just love bald guys.

01:35.596 --> 01:37.426
[laughs]

01:37.472 --> 01:40.772
- Yeah, well, they also say
it ain’t the size that counts.

01:40.809 --> 01:45.359
So I wouldn’t worry about those
pathetic stick arms of yours.

01:45.397 --> 01:47.357
- I don’t have stick arms.

01:47.399 --> 01:50.239
- Hey, do I know you?

01:51.528 --> 01:54.778
- Get back in your boxes,
all of you!

01:54.823 --> 01:56.873
Don’t make me come back there!

01:57.409 --> 02:00.329
- She is fuckin’ hot.

02:00.370 --> 02:02.370
- Oh, forget it, Sticky.

02:02.414 --> 02:05.634
Chicks like that need
someone more...

02:05.667 --> 02:06.997
I don’t know...

02:07.044 --> 02:08.964
virile?

02:09.004 --> 02:11.714
- Does that guy look familiar?

02:11.757 --> 02:15.257
- Yeah.
Come to think of it, he does.

02:15.302 --> 02:17.012
- I can’t put my finger on it.

02:17.054 --> 02:19.434
He’s just, like...

02:19.473 --> 02:22.143
repulsive or something.

02:22.184 --> 02:23.694
- He sure is.

02:24.936 --> 02:26.226
- They don’t know me.

02:26.271 --> 02:28.901
<i>[tense music]</i>

02:28.940 --> 02:30.230
They don’t know you, either.

02:31.068 --> 02:33.238
[both screaming]

02:33.278 --> 02:35.948
- I’m done with you, Chucky,

02:35.989 --> 02:38.909
and your tiny fuckin’ dick!

02:38.950 --> 02:40.330
- [gasps]

02:41.078 --> 02:42.788
- They weren’t there.

02:44.289 --> 02:45.749
And they don’t know
what you did.

02:45.791 --> 02:48.711
- You just keep your mouth
shut, buster, or I’ll--

02:48.752 --> 02:49.592
[tires screeching]

02:49.628 --> 02:50.708
[Tiffany gasps]
[gunshot]

02:50.754 --> 02:51.884
[horns blaring]

02:53.340 --> 02:59.260
<i>♪ ♪</i>

03:01.723 --> 03:03.603
[all gasp]

03:03.642 --> 03:08.902
