03:08.939 --> 03:10.439
- Andy.

03:11.650 --> 03:12.820
Get him!

03:12.859 --> 03:19.819
<i>♪ ♪</i>

03:26.832 --> 03:28.212
- Shit.

03:30.794 --> 03:32.174
- [cackles]

03:33.130 --> 03:34.300
- [gasps]

03:35.132 --> 03:37.302
- [cackling]

