[grunting]

03:47.018 --> 03:47.978
[engine revs]

03:48.019 --> 03:49.599
[tires screeching]

03:50.021 --> 03:54.901
<i>♪ ♪</i>

03:54.943 --> 03:56.693
- This is for Kyle!

03:56.737 --> 04:02.447
<i>♪ ♪</i>

04:02.492 --> 04:05.702
[all screaming]

04:08.165 --> 04:10.925
