- Hey.

05:16.775 --> 05:18.075
- Hey.

05:18.109 --> 05:24.619
<i>♪ ♪</i>

05:24.658 --> 05:27.448
- So, uh, I guess this is it.

05:27.494 --> 05:30.504
- Well, only for now.
I mean,

05:30.539 --> 05:32.579
I only live two hours away,

05:32.624 --> 05:34.834
and I can see you
every weekend.

05:34.876 --> 05:36.786
- Jake...

05:36.837 --> 05:38.377
you know
that’s not gonna happen.

05:39.381 --> 05:41.671
- [sighs] I know.

05:43.468 --> 05:45.678
- It wouldn’t be enough,
anyway.

05:45.720 --> 05:47.760
- I know.

05:47.806 --> 05:50.346
You know, at this point,
I’ll take what we can get.

05:50.392 --> 05:53.102
<i>- ♪ This ain’t no lullaby ♪</i>

05:53.144 --> 05:54.854
[car horn honks]

05:57.524 --> 06:00.694
- Let’s go, Batman!
To the Batcave!

06:00.735 --> 06:03.395
- [chuckles]
On my way, Robin!

06:03.446 --> 06:05.236
- You got a fellow foster
this time.

06:05.282 --> 06:08.032
- Uh, yeah. He seems okay.

06:09.661 --> 06:12.251
