15:05.029 --> 15:07.489
- No, the douchebag.

15:07.532 --> 15:11.992
<i>♪ ♪</i>

15:12.036 --> 15:13.326
<i>[doorbell dings]</i>

15:13.371 --> 15:14.371
What the hell?

15:18.376 --> 15:20.036
<i>- Trick or treat.
</i> <i>Smell my feet.</i>

15:20.086 --> 15:22.296
<i>Give me something good to eat.
</i> - Oh, no.

15:25.842 --> 15:29.682
<i>- That’s not very scary.
What are you supposed to be?</i>

15:29.720 --> 15:31.970
<i>- The ghost of Halloween past.</i>

15:32.014 --> 15:34.274
<i>Say hello to my friends.
</i> - Oh, shit. No.

15:34.308 --> 15:35.478
<i>- Hi.</i>

15:37.145 --> 15:39.105
<i>- Could I please use
</i> <i>your bathroom?</i>

15:39.147 --> 15:41.067
<i>It’s an emergency.
</i> <i>[phone chimes]</i>

15:41.107 --> 15:42.937
- No! Caroline, no!
<i>- Um--</i>

15:42.984 --> 15:45.034
- Look, she can’t hear us.
He muted us.

15:45.069 --> 15:46.489
<i>- Okay. It’s upstairs.
