15:46.529 --> 15:47.819
Devon, wait.
Use your landline.

15:47.864 --> 15:49.534
Call the police.
I’m gonna call Lexy.

15:49.574 --> 15:50.824
- Jake, they’re not gonna
listen to me.

15:50.867 --> 15:52.027
- Just don’t mention Chucky!

15:52.076 --> 15:53.196
Just get someone over there!

15:53.244 --> 15:54.584
- Okay.

15:54.620 --> 15:56.710
<i>[suspenseful music]</i>

15:56.747 --> 15:59.077
<i>[line trilling]</i>

16:01.252 --> 16:02.292
- Shit, shit, shit.

16:06.340 --> 16:08.930
- Yes, I’d like to report
a break-in at 3083 Fairburn.

16:10.344 --> 16:12.104
