just two feet tall.

33:53.990 --> 33:56.830
- Short people can be assholes.

33:56.868 --> 33:58.748
- I don’t know, maybe.

34:00.830 --> 34:03.580
Yeah, are you okay?

34:03.625 --> 34:05.715
- Yeah, I’m fine. Why?

