and your idiot BFFs

36:50.500 --> 36:52.920
falling right into my trap.

36:53.837 --> 36:57.127
See, I needed the three of you
to get back together

36:57.173 --> 37:00.013
so I could kill you
all at once.

37:00.051 --> 37:02.431
But you never got
back together.

37:02.470 --> 37:04.640
So much for BFFs.

37:04.681 --> 37:06.971
I hang out
with my murder victims

37:07.016 --> 37:09.726
more often than you assholes
see each other.

37:11.104 --> 37:13.064
- We’ve been busy.
- Yeah?

37:13.106 --> 37:16.896
Well, now, you’re all gonna
get busy dyin’,

37:16.943 --> 37:20.243
