37:30.915 --> 37:33.165
- Just let the kids go.

37:33.209 --> 37:36.169
- Nah. The more, the merrier.

37:36.212 --> 37:37.842
- Why are you doing this?

37:37.881 --> 37:41.181
- There were 72 of me
on that truck.

37:41.217 --> 37:42.677
