take over the world,

37:42.719 --> 37:44.509
and I would’ve gotten away
with it, too,

37:44.554 --> 37:47.724
if it weren’t for you
meddling kids

37:47.766 --> 37:49.636
and Andy

37:49.684 --> 37:54.774
and that goddamn bitch
from hell, Tiffany.

37:54.814 --> 37:59.364
I’m gonna kill
every last one of you.

38:00.487 --> 38:03.317
- Wait, exactly how many
of you are left?

38:03.364 --> 38:06.704
- Enough to make this
worth the sacrifice.

38:06.743 --> 38:10.333
I die knowing
I took all of you with me.

38:10.371 --> 38:13.871
You die knowing
I never really die.

38:13.917 --> 38:15.787
[chuckles]

38:15.835 --> 38:19.955
Just as soon
as Lexy gets down here.

38:20.006 --> 38:23.966
- [sniffing]

38:24.010 --> 38:30.890
