[bomb beeps]

40:01.482 --> 40:03.362
[Gary screams]

40:07.572 --> 40:09.452
[Chucky giggles]

40:13.620 --> 40:15.790
- There’s no pain greater

40:15.830 --> 40:17.750
than the permanent grief

40:17.790 --> 40:20.460
that a parent suffers
after the loss of a child.

40:22.211 --> 40:26.511
